room_title: Escape room "Creature Room 2016" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
room_description:
A dark and rainy night. Your car breaks down on a remote road. The house at the top of the hill has a flickering light. When you knock on the door it pushes open. You hear a noise and call out to ask to use the phone. The door slams shut behind you...
You're now locked in the house. There is a clock in the room that says dinner time is 60 minutes away. You don't know what or who lives here, but you know you don't want to be there for dinner!
